title: Roscoe Wallace, Serena Williams, PVAMU, Steve Comedy Question and more.
itunes:title: Roscoe Wallace, Serena Williams, PVAMU, Steve Comedy Question and more.
description:
Good morning and welcome to the ride!  Somebody's back and it's Humpday.  The CLO wants to know what happens at a sex toy party really?  Fentanyl was confiscated at LAX and a countrywide warning was issued by law enforcement for parents on Halloween.  Lyft is offering a 50% percent off discount for rides to the polls.  The greatest lounge sanger Roscoe Wallace gives us his opinion on Drake's 36th birthday party.  PVAMU AND TAMU wins BIG!  WTH is going on with The Lakers?  Serena stepping away from tennis sparked thee question for Steve.  Today the show wraps up a bit short and Steve is being hella extra with it, btw.
